name: Yilon_Kres
content:
Yilon Kres was a female Rodian who supervised Warehouse 305 during the Clone Wars. She was part of the black market network on Mandalore.
Yilon Kres was mentioned in Collapse of the Republic, a roleplaying supplementary sourcebook for the Star Wars Roleplaying series that was published by Fantasy Flight Games in 2019.
